\"><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529162\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529162\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 21, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104kdf1665703258460.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kdf1665703258460.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/kdf1665703258460.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"kdf1665703258460\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"kdf1665703258460___entities__472593\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The [entities] section of the initialization file is used to set widget properties for entities in Form components. It can be used to style the default entity widget, but it is also possible set properties for specific entities, or for an entity in a specific component.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"kdf1665703258460__topic_d144896e1_d144897e1_d144898e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kdf1665703258460__p_d144899e1_d144900e1_d144901e1\">Each entry in this section has the following syntax:</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kdf1665703258460__p_d144902e1_d144903e1_d144904e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>{<var class=\"keyword varname\">.Model</var>{<var class=\"keyword varname\">.ComponentName</var>}}<code class=\"ph codeph\">=udefentity(</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Properties</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">)</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kdf1665703258460__topic_d103917e1_d103918e1_d103919e1_d103920e1_d103921e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1076023e80\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kdf1665703258460__li_d50456e1_d50457e1_d50458e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var>—name of an entity. The\n               default name for all entities is <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">DefEntity</span>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kdf1665703258460__li_d50459e1_d50460e1_d50461e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Model</var>—name of the application\n               model to which <var class=\"keyword varname\">Entity</var> belongs. If not specified, properties are\n               applied to the default widget of all entities with the same name, regardless of the\n               model to which they belong. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kdf1665703258460__li_d50462e1_d50463e1_d50464e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">ComponentName</var>—name of a\n               component in which the entity occurs. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"kdf1665703258460__li_d50465e1_d50466e1_d50467e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Properties</var>—semi-colon\n               separated string of property-value pairs. The maximum length is 1024 characters. For\n               more information, see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"uvn1665702612860.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/uvn1665702612860.html\" title=\"Logical widget for styling the default entity widget udefentity in Form components. The properties set are applied to all entities in the application. If DefEntity is not defined, the udefentity widget is transparent and follows Windows conventions.\">DefEntity</a>. </li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"kdf1665703258460__topic_d103922e1_d103923e1_d103924e1_d103925e1_d103926e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1076023e128\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kdf1665703258460__p_d144911e1_d144912e1_d144913e1\">To define the default widget properties for the default entity widget on Windows, use the <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">DefEntity</span> setting.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"kdf1665703258460__p_d144914e1_d144915e1_d144916e1\">You can override this setting for specific entities by adding definitions in the [entities] section. For example:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">[entities]\nentstyle_0=udefentity(bordertype=flat)\nentstyle_1.dummy=udefentity(backimage=@../images/sky.png;valign=center;halign=center)\nperson.org.FRM_CONTACT=udefentity(bordertype=flat;backcolor=blue;borderradius=20px)</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529162\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529162\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "[entities] Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 21, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 The [entities] section of the initialization file is used to set widget properties for entities in Form components. It can be used to style the default entity widget, but it is also possible set properties for specific entities, or for an entity in a specific component. Each entry in this section has the following syntax: Entity { .Model { .ComponentName }} =udefentity( Properties ) Arguments Entity —name of an entity. The default name for all entities is DefEntity . Model —name of the application model to which Entity belongs. If not specified, properties are applied to the default widget of all entities with the same name, regardless of the model to which they belong. ComponentName —name of a component in which the entity occurs. Properties —semi-colon separated string of property-value pairs. The maximum length is 1024 characters. For more information, see DefEntity . Description To define the default widget properties for the default entity widget on Windows, use the DefEntity setting. You can override this setting for specific entities by adding definitions in the [entities] section. For example: [entities] entstyle_0=udefentity(bordertype=flat) entstyle_1.dummy=udefentity(backimage=@../images/sky.png;valign=center;halign=center) person.org.FRM_CONTACT=udefentity(bordertype=flat;backcolor=blue;borderradius=20px) Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}